          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and it’s especially painful to see kids suffering from its ravages. That’s what makes Rides to Remember, an annual event Ferrari of Atlanta has put on for the past 15 years, so phenomenal. The ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
